chan = Rails.configuration.slack_channels.horizons_equinox

header "🌗 welcome to equinox!"

section <<~TEXT, markdown: true
  You've just been added to <##{chan}>, the channel for Horizons Equinox in Africa! For more info, check out [horizons.hackclub.com/equinox](https://horizons.hackclub.com/equinox).

  Head over and introduce yourself!
TEXT
